languages.text: "Облагодательствовали вы отсек своим визитом, Лорд-капитан. Благословили палубу, так сказать, своей драгоценной ножкой".
"You've graced the compartment with your presence, Lord Captain. Blessed the deck, so to speak, with your noble foot."

languages.text: “领主舰长，您的莅临让这片甲板蓬荜生辉。可以说，您高贵的双脚为这片甲板带来了祝福。”
languages.original_text: "You've graced the compartment with your presence, Lord Captain. Blessed the deck, so to speak, with your noble foot."

languages.text: "Ihr habt das Modul mit Eurer Anwesenheit beehrt, Lord Captain. Habt das Deck sozusagen mit Eurem edlen Fuß gesegnet."
